&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The MDU Growth Lead is responsible for leading, coaching, and developing the Bay Area MDU Growth team in support of Sonic’s fiber sales initiatives within multi-dwelling unit (MDU) communities. This role combines frontline sales leadership with hands-on field execution, including canvassing, side-by-side selling, sales coaching, and performance accountability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a motivated field leader who can inspire and develop team members while driving consistent sales results. This individual will support daily sales execution, provide real-time coaching and feedback, identify growth opportunities, and communicate actionable insights and reporting to the MDU Sales Market Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Type/Expected Hours of Work:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
