&lt;li&gt;Drive performance accountability through goal setting, coaching, and follow-up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor individual and team sales metrics, productivity, and daily activity levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide timely reporting, sales updates, and field insights to the MDU Sales Market Manager&lt;/li&gt;
