&lt;li&gt;Assist with escalations, account concerns, and field-related issues as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure team adherence to company policies, safety procedures, and brand standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Sonic professionally and positively within the communities we serve&lt;/li&gt;
