&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sonic&#39;s &lt;strong&gt;SAP Functional Lead &lt;/strong&gt;serves as our internal subject matter expert, combining deep finance and accounting functional expertise with IT administration capabilities. This role bridges finance, IT, and operations teams to optimize our SAP investment, build internal capability, and reduce dependency on external consultants. The position is critical to supporting our financial close processes, managing system security and workflows, and driving continuous improvement of our ERP platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Type/Expected Hours of Work:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time (40 hours per week), exempt/salaried position. Occasional evening or weekend work may be required during month-end/year-end close periods or system updates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Minimal travel required. Occasional travel to company offices or SAP training events (less than 10% annually).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supervisory Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position has no direct reports but will coordinate work with external SAP consulting partners and provide guidance to end users across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Duties and Responsibilities: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Finance &amp;amp; Accounting Focus (Primary)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as functional expert for SAP S/4HANA Public Cloud Finance modules, including Financial Accounting (FI), Controlling (CO), Revenue Accounting and Reporting (RAR), and Asset Accounting (AA)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support month-end and year-end close processes, financial reporting requirements, and audit activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure and maintain revenue recognition processes in compliance with ASC 606/IFRS 15 standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize chart of accounts, cost centers, profit centers, and financial reporting structures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support subscription billing and recurring revenue management business processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with CFO, Controller, and accounting team on system enhancements and process improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
